context:
KR:
&lt;히스클리프, 정신이 들어?&gt;
EN:
&lt;Are you okay, Heathcliff?&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#c29a5f&gt;드디어.&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#c29a5f&gt;At last.&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#c29a5f&gt;모두가 한자리에 모였구나.&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#c29a5f&gt;You are all gathered here.&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#c29a5f&gt;부디 이번만큼은 다툼 없이, 나의 말을 존중해 주길.&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#c29a5f&gt;My only wish is that my words will be met with respect, without hostility among you.&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#c29a5f&gt;화를 내는 사람은 없었으면 좋겠어. 이건 한 번뿐인 내 장례식이잖아.&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#c29a5f&gt;I hope that none of you become incensed during this occasion. It's my one and only funeral, after all.&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#c29a5f&gt;그리고 지금의 나는 전혀 고통스럽거나 괴롭지도 않아.&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#c29a5f&gt;I am at peace; there is no pain, no suffering where I am.&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#c29a5f&gt;그러니 내 죽음을 안타깝게 생각하는 일도 없었으면 해.&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#c29a5f&gt;So do not consider my death a tragic one.&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#c29a5f&gt;나는 나만의 천국에 이르렀을 거니까.&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#c29a5f&gt;Because by the time you are hearing this, I must have reached my own heaven.&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#c29a5f&gt;하지만 그렇다고 해서 슬퍼하지 말라는 건 아니야.&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#c29a5f&gt;This is not to say that you mustn't let sorrow into your hearts.&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#c29a5f&gt;눈물은 마음껏 흘려.&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#c29a5f&gt;Weep, if you will.&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#c29a5f&gt;그래야 날 진심으로 사랑한다는 마음이 느껴질 테니까.&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#c29a5f&gt;So that I may feel your grief and know that you have all truly loved me.&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#c29a5f&gt;워더링하이츠. 낡고 황량한 저택.&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#c29a5f&gt;Wuthering Heights. An old and desolate manor.&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#c29a5f&gt;난 이곳을 많이 무서워했지. 매일같이 악몽을 꾸고 겁에 질려했지만…&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#c29a5f&gt;I have always been afraid of this place. Fear and nightmares would consume me every night.&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#c29a5f&gt;이제야… 죽음에 이르러서야, 이 저택을 있는 그대로 받아들이기로 했어.&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#c29a5f&gt;... But now that I stand before the end of my life, I have come to accept this manor for what it is.&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#c29a5f&gt;이제 이 저택을…&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#c29a5f&gt;This manor, which I will leave...&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#c29a5f&gt;나의 남편, 린튼 에드가에게 남길게.&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#c29a5f&gt;... to my husband, Linton Edgar.&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#c29a5f&gt;나를 계속 기억하며, 이 저택을 소유해 줘.&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#c29a5f&gt;Keep this manor, and remember me by its presence.&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#c29a5f&gt;그리고, 하나뿐인 내 오빠, 힌들리.&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#c29a5f&gt;And my brother, Hindley. My one and only brother.&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#c29a5f&gt;빚이 매우 많은 상황이라고 들었어.&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#c29a5f&gt;I heard that you are mired in quite the heavy debt.&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#c29a5f&gt;매일같이 술과 도박을 일삼고 있다는 것도.&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#c29a5f&gt;And that you have been spending most of your days drinking and gambling.&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#c29a5f&gt;그래서 나는…&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#c29a5f&gt;So I...&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#c29a5f&gt;M사에 있는 어비스 트라우마 교정실에 오빠를 등록해 놓았어.&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#c29a5f&gt;... signed you up for the 'Abyss Trauma Correctional Facility' at M Corp.&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#c29a5f&gt;이 말을 듣고, 일주일 내에 방문을 해서 서류를 접수하지 않으면…&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#c29a5f&gt;If you don't visit the facility within 1 week after attending this will-reading...&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#c29a5f&gt;그쪽에서 오빠를 찾으러 직접 방문할 거야.&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#c29a5f&gt;... they will come to take you in.&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#c29a5f&gt;오빠의 마음이 건강해질 수 있기를 진심으로 빌게.&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#c29a5f&gt;I truly hope that your heart will be healed, dear brother.&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#c29a5f&gt;물론 오빠를 위해 M사로 가는 워프 열차 이용권도 준비해 두었으니 걱정은 마.&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#c29a5f&gt;Of course, I have already prepared a WARP train ticket to M Corp. for you, so please don't worry about the travel fees.&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#c29a5f&gt;그리고 히스클리프.&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#c29a5f&gt;And you, Heathcliff.&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#c29a5f&gt;집으로 온 걸 환영해.&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#c29a5f&gt;Welcome home.&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#c29a5f&gt;이 저택에… 일곱 번의 벼락이 치고 난 후.&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#c29a5f&gt;Once the seventh strike of lightning falls upon this manor...&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#c29a5f&gt;그 후엔, 황금가지가 네 것이 될 거야.&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#c29a5f&gt;... my Golden Bough shall be yours.&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;…….&gt;
EN:
&lt;…….&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#c29a5f&gt;내가 소유한 그 황금가지를 너에게 줄게. 히스클리프.&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#c29a5f&gt;I will leave my Golden Bough to you, Heathcliff.&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;하나가 아니야…&gt;
EN:
&lt;It's not 'a' Golden Bough...&gt;

KR:
&lt;황금가지가… 한 개가 더 있어, 이 저택에.&gt;
EN:
&lt;There is... a second Golden Bough in this manor.&gt;
